        <h1 class="heading text-xl md:text-2xl">PRIVACY STATEMENT</h1>
        <h3 class="font-bold mt-3 mb-1 text-xl">WHAT DO WE DO WITH YOUR INFORMATION?</h3>
        <p>When you register on our website, or purchase something from our store, as part of the buying process, we collect the personal information you give us such as your name or your family member’s name, age, address, your email ID, your mobile number, referral details, gifting details and any other information shared by you.</p>
        <p>When you browse our website, we also automatically receive your computer or mobile phone’s internet protocol (IP) address in order to provide us with information that helps us learn about your browser and operating system.</p>
        <p>Email marketing, SMS updates, App Push notifications and any other communication: Your submission of contact information is considered as deemed approval and acceptance to share regular updates, information about our store, new products and other updates.</p>
